Merge branch 'openssl_3'

Simplify the CPU count detection.

On Apple silicon, calling system_profiler SPHardwareDataType returns more
than a single number, it appends the performance/efficiency core counts.

Example on Apple silicon:
      Total Number of Cores: 8 (4 performance and 4 efficiency)

To simplify everything, just switch to sysctl which just gives a raw number.
